data.text:
Finally! I just discovered it myself when I was going around doing my usually drama rounds. And lisette mentioned it in a earlier post. I've personally become one of those people who are too lazy to download, so I thought I could make a good note of it here for me and everyone in the community.

You guys can watch it here!

It seems like the dramas for next season are set and Kassy is not involved in any of them. Perhaps next season. :)

do you love? | 4 loves | Share | Flag | Link

Double hitter of Kassy and Nagase and i've not yet watched it. How crazy is that?!

And Kassy COULD be in next season... I mean, not all the dramas are completely casted so we can only live in hope. VERY little hope but it will happen soon enough!

Reply | Thread | Link

I'm watching it RIGHT NOW and my exams are in two days. D: But with Hakusen Nagashi, I promised myself that I wanted to watch it before I graduate... so at least I could relate it. Something I need done before I get out of high school. I really like it so far.

I suppose another miracle COULD happen. Like how Okada's SP was decided last minute.
